title: Episode 77 | Honestly, We're In Mexico
description: Buenos Días! This week the guys are in Mexico talking about Drake's new album, having Logic on the Pod, meeting Adam Sandler, Beyonce's album dropping, Joey Badass moving his album release, real-life Squid Games, robots catching feels, the 2022 XXL list, and much more!
author: newrorymal@gmail.com (More Sauce)
